# Workspace & Package Management

- **Always use the latest possible version** when adding packages. Check pub.dev; use the newest version compatible with project constraints
- In a Dart workspace monorepo: run `flutter pub get` from root for workspace deps; run `dart pub get` only inside server directories (e.g. `merchant_clowder_server/`)
- Add dependencies only to the appropriate package directory (do not add at root)
- Use `flutter pub add <package_name>` for regular deps, `flutter pub add dev:<package_name>` for dev deps
- Document the reason when using an older version due to incompatibility
